# Invoice OCR Project

# Project Structure

-   `data/` - raw and processed invoices
-   `src/` - source code modules
-   `notebooks/` - experiments and development
-   `configs/` - YAML configuration files
-   `tests/` - unit tests

# Description

Pipeline for preprocessing scanned invoices:

-   Denoising
-   Gamma correction
-   CLAHE (local contrast)
-   Linear brightening
-   Deskew (Hough lines)
-   Orientation normalization (±90° / 180°)

# Usage

```python
from src.preprocessing.pipeline import preprocess_invoice_pipeline

processed_img = preprocess_invoice_pipeline(
    "data/raw/invoice_original.png",
    "data/processed/invoice_preprocessed.png",
    rotate_180=True
)
```
